  <p class="text-text-muted text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 !mt-0">Grinduro Format</p>
  <p>This isn&apos;t a time trial. It&apos;s a mass-start sufferfest with structure.</p>
  <p>
    <strong class="text-accent-white">Seven gravel sectors</strong> are timed &mdash;
    rated 1&ndash;5 stars by surface brutality, Paris-Roubaix style.
    <strong class="text-accent-green">Three KOM/QOM climbs</strong> are timed separately &mdash;
    fastest up takes the segment.
  </p>
  <p>
    Everything between? Challenging, remote, and utterly untimed.
    Ride your own ride. Race the sectors. Suffer together.
  </p>
